{"arkId":"cl010095714","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010095714","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"La Com\u00e9die","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"La Com\u00e9die"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1868 - 1874","currentLocation":"[SCULPT] Jardin des Tuileries","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1868,"endYear":1874,"imprecision":"","text":"XIXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Roux, Julien Toussaint","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1836","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1880","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q97768256"},{"label":"France","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"TU 348","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"Sculptures des jardins","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"statue","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"2,24","displayDimension":"2,24 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"0,85","displayDimension":"0,85 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"0,7","displayDimension":"0,7 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"marbre, marbre blanc","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Roux a d\u2019abord cr\u00e9\u00e9 cette all\u00e9gorie de la com\u00e9die antique pour le d\u00e9cor du Grand Th\u00e9\u00e2tre d\u2019Angers. La commande lui est pass\u00e9e en 1868 par l\u2019architecte Auguste Magne. La statue en pierre est en place pour l\u2019inauguration de l\u2019\u00e9difice le 11 novembre 1871 (toujours visible sur la fa\u00e7ade, 1er \u00e9tage, 2e niche \u00e0 partir de la droite). En 1872, Roux expose le pl\u00e2tre au Salon des artistes fran\u00e7ais (n\u00b0 1838) puis un marbre au Salon de 1874 (n\u00b0 3127). Le sculpteur obtient que le marbre soit acquis par l\u2019Etat (arr\u00eat\u00e9 du 5 juin 1874), pour 6 000 francs (somme qu\u2019il juge trop faible). Il est rapport\u00e9 du palais de l\u2019Industrie (aux Champs-Elys\u00e9es, o\u00f9 se tient le Salon) pour \u00eatre install\u00e9 au jardin des Tuileries le 16 janvier 1875, sur le socle jusqu\u2019alors occup\u00e9 par le Philop\u0153men de David d\u2019Angers.\r\nLe pl\u00e2tre du Salon de 1872 a \u00e9t\u00e9 donn\u00e9 par l\u2019artiste en 1875 au mus\u00e9e des Beaux-Arts d\u2019Angers : il n\u2019est plus localis\u00e9.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"achat par l\u0027\u00c9tat","doubt":"","dates":[]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"achat par l\u0027\u00c9tat"}],"material":[{"value":"marbre"},{"value":"marbre blanc"}],"objectType":[{"value":"statue"}]},"bibliography":[],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000095714\/0000258875_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000095714\/0000258875_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2007 Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, Dist. GrandPalaisRmn \/ Pierre Philibert","type":"","position":0},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000095714\/0000258876_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre